@node MAIN "Welcome"

@{JCENTER}


 @{b}@{fg shine}MacOS X collection of graphics for AmigaOS@{fg text}@{ub}@{LINE}


 This small guide will help you to preview and show you how to install graphics for some of the Amiga's most popular programs.@{LINE}
 My graphics set is inspired by the MacOS X - the best operating system Your money can buy!@{LINE}

 For all comments and suggestions write to:  @{bg shine}mexico@ptt.yu @{bg back} ( Miki Radulovic )


